american radio " sawa " today , sunday , quoted these sources as saying that the united states might approve the implementation of this plan as a unilateral phase by israel in implementing the american road map . they added that there is a congruence of opinions between israel and the united states that the palestinian prime minister ahmad qureia abu al ala ' cannot resume negotiations with israel and therefore israel must find another way to break the political standstill in the israeli - palestinian course .
at the same level , sources at the office of israeli prime minister ariel sharon said that israel will intensify the activity of the special team headed by major general geora elen in order to complete the preparation of the unilateral disengagement plan in the west bank .
the sources added that sharon will present this plan to american president george bush in their meeting scheduled in washington next february .
iraqi commerce bank collects export guarantees for reconstruction companies
baghdad , january 25 / xinhua / the iraqi commerce bank , established by the united states , obtained two billion and four hundred million american dollars as export guarantees for companies that are willing to make deals as part of iraqi 's reconstruction process .
al arabia news channel said this evening , sunday , that the bank issued approximately one hundred and thirty letters of credit valued at three hundred million dollars . the bank also started receiving requests from seventeen international agencies for export credit .
al arabia channel said that a consortium of banks presented export credit with reserves totaling approximately five billion dollars .
